1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:45,740
=Episode 20=

16
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:48,959
Pengyu.

17
00:01:50,079 --> 00:01:50,920
It's been a while.

18
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,639
You really are Donghai's son.

19
00:02:14,879 --> 00:02:15,759
You know...

20
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,360
I don't appreciate it when people throw

21
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,759
my father's name around.

22
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,039
Especially you.

23
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,599
If all you wanted was
a piece of the pie,

24
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:28,199
that's fine.

25
00:02:28,759 --> 00:02:29,960
You've made your profit.

26
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:31,680
Let's leave it at that.

27
00:02:33,599 --> 00:02:34,680
The whole world thinks

28
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:36,240
I'm just some

29
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,719
insignificant,

30
00:02:37,759 --> 00:02:39,039
unreliable nobody.

31
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:41,360
It seems you're just as naive, Mr. Jiang,

32
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,560
to think this pittance

33
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,680
is enough to make me go away.

34
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:46,840
I know exactly how badly

35
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,319
you want to sink your teeth

36
00:02:48,319 --> 00:02:49,560
into Bosi Real Estate.

37
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,120
You don't want any competition.

38
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,479
But I want to fight you for it.

39
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,000
Because I want a taste, too.

40
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,080
If you're

41
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,240
doing this for your father,

42
00:02:57,680 --> 00:03:00,400
you didn't know
the kind of man Xian Donghai is...

43
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,120
I told you.

44
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:03,639
Keep my father's name out of your mouth.

45
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,199
Whether I knew my father or not

46
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,280
is none of your business.

47
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,599
I just want you

48
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:11,520
to see exactly how

49
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:13,240
an "insignificant, unreliable nobody"

50
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,599
like me

51
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:15,840
can snatch away

52
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,360
the prize

53
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:19,080
you thought was already

54
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,439
in the bag.

55
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,639
Fair enough.

56
00:03:30,159 --> 00:03:30,879
By the way,

57
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:32,759
Mr. Jiang.

58
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,300
Do you get an annual checkup?

59
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,319
How's your heart?

60
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:42,000
Have you ever seen someone

61
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,560
suffocate during a sudden heart attack?

62
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:48,919
You haven't,

63
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,840
but I have.

64
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,439
It's over in a flash.

65
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:56,960
Just a few seconds,

66
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:58,439
and the face

67
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,719
turns a deep shade of purple

68
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,919
like an eggplant.

69
00:04:07,159 --> 00:04:07,960
The eyes too.

70
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,719
The pupils dilate,

71
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,759
bloodshot.

72
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,919
The body locks up,

73
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,480
mouth wide open.

74
00:04:17,759 --> 00:04:20,680
As if in their final breath, they were
trying to scream something out.

75
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,959
But they couldn't

76
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:24,639
make a sound.

77
00:04:25,300 --> 00:04:33,940
(Mourning the Passing
of Mr. Xian Donghai)

78
00:04:37,639 --> 00:04:38,959
Everyone wonders

79
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:40,399
what his last words

80
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:42,639
were meant to be.

81
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:44,519
But I don't wonder at all.

82
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:46,079
You know why?

83
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:47,959
Because what I'm really curious about

84
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:49,079
is you, Jiang Dongchao.

85
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:50,160
What will your last words be

86
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,480
when your time comes?

87
00:04:55,759 --> 00:04:56,600
Xian Pengyu.

88
00:04:59,759 --> 00:05:01,480
Do you have any idea what you're doing?

89
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,279
Absolutely.

90
00:05:09,279 --> 00:05:11,600
Hyenas hunting for food

91
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,600
have to wait for

92
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,120
the perfect opportunity.

93
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,279
While big shots like you

94
00:05:17,279 --> 00:05:18,680
are busy plundering,

95
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:19,920
you tend to overlook

96
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,759
scavengers like us,

97
00:05:20,759 --> 00:05:21,800
hyenas watching you

98
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:23,319
from the shadows.

99
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,959
Don't underestimate a hyena.

100
00:05:26,839 --> 00:05:27,920
They're vicious.

101
00:05:28,639 --> 00:05:29,800
Just a few of them

102
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:31,319
can tear apart

103
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:35,120
a full-grown lion.

104
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:40,519
Isn't that right, Xiongshi Fund?

105
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:49,360
Good to see you again.

106
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:50,759
Goodbye.

107
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,040
My father acquired
Yinghuo Shipping back then.

108
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,600
And you?

109
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,759
Now you're taking over Bosi Real Estate.

110
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,720
History has a funny way

111
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,120
of repeating itself.

112
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,079
Mr. Jiang,

113
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,720
let's see what happens.

114
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,240
In the very near future,

115
00:06:07,519 --> 00:06:08,879
the son of your best friend,

116
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,279
Xian Donghai,

117
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,879
is going to be the one

118
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,879
who tears you down.

119
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,360
The pills...

120
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,480
(Fast-Acting Heart Tabs)

121
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,879
are ready for you.

122
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:29,279
I'll take the medicine.

123
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,800
Much appreciated.

124
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:31,639
Don't mention it.

125
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,520
You'd better
keep a dose for yourself, too.

126
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:36,639
Never underestimate
the power of genetics.

127
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,480
Farewell.

128
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:39,959
I just warmed this up.

129
00:07:39,959 --> 00:07:41,000
It's a bit hot.

130
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:47,199
Who washed my handkerchief?

131
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,319
What?

132
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:49,439
Who washed it?

133
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,279
It must have been the new maid.

134
00:07:53,519 --> 00:07:54,519
I forgot to tell her...

135
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,399
I'm sorry.

136
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:59,000
Did I not make it clear?

137
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,680
No one touches this handkerchief.

138
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,439
I'm so sorry.

139
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:04,439
I'm sorry.

140
00:08:06,519 --> 00:08:07,319
Forgive me.

141
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:10,600
I'm really sorry.

142
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:18,639
No...

143
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:20,199
Please, don't.

144
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,040
No.

145
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:24,160
The girl is still awake.

146
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:25,959
Please, don't hit me.

147
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,240
The girl is still awake.

148
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,399
I'm sorry.

149
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:54,039
Daddy?

150
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,120
Chloe.

151
00:09:03,279 --> 00:09:05,399
Daddy, was Mommy being bad again?

152
00:09:07,399 --> 00:09:08,080
I'm sorry.

153
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:10,240
Mommy was naughty again.

154
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:12,200
Yeah.

155
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,799
But Chloe is a good girl,

156
00:09:14,799 --> 00:09:15,480
right?

157
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,559
Let's go to sleep, okay?

158
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:18,840
Okay.

159
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:23,200
Alright.

160
00:09:24,879 --> 00:09:26,480
Such a good girl.

161
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,960
The cow jumped over the moon.

162
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:44,000
And there are three little bears
sitting on chairs.

163
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:46,200
Goodnight, bears.

164
00:09:46,759 --> 00:09:48,480
Bears, goodnight.

165
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:51,320
And goodnight, chairs.

166
00:09:51,820 --> 00:09:53,340
- Hush.
- Hush.

167
00:09:55,759 --> 00:09:58,759
Alright, time to sleep.

168
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,120
Daddy.

169
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:02,200
Can I sleep with you

170
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,399
and Mommy tonight?

171
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,720
I'm scared.

172
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:08,120
What are you afraid of?

173
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:10,200
The monsters.

174
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:14,519
Chloe, baby...

175
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,200
listen to me.

176
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,799
No one in this world

177
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:19,000
is going to

178
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,679
truly help you but yourself.

179
00:10:22,279 --> 00:10:23,320
If you don't want

180
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,639
to be hurt by monsters,

181
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:27,879
then you have to

182
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:29,200
become a monster yourself.

183
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,320
Do you understand?

184
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:31,960
Okay.

185
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:32,879
That's my girl.

186
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,559
Goodnight. Love you.

187
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,600
I heard the news.

188
00:10:43,279 --> 00:10:44,080
Xian Pengyu

189
00:10:45,679 --> 00:10:46,879
shut down your food street.

190
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:49,679
It's such a shame.

191
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,120
I'm still fighting for it.

192
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:53,919
Yuci.

193
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,000
Come back to Lysen Group.

194
00:11:02,279 --> 00:11:03,080
To be honest,

195
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:06,039
I've always wanted to help you.

196
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,559
We could help each other.

197
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:16,240
I heard you also suspended

198
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:18,120
the Green Building
Materials acquisition.

199
00:11:19,039 --> 00:11:20,399
I've been waiting for your return.

200
00:11:21,879 --> 00:11:22,799
This project

201
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,440
was your proposal.

202
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:25,840
I wouldn't trust

203
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,519
anyone else to handle it.

204
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:31,519
You uncovered
the truth about Li Qiang's death.

205
00:11:32,519 --> 00:11:33,399
Mr. Li

206
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:35,159
wants you back, too.

207
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,240
Yuci.

208
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:40,200
You have so many dreams.

209
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,990
Lysen Group and I can
help you achieve them all.

210
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:51,100
(Xinkang Treatment Center)

211
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:54,159
No one was supposed to know
I was staying here.

212
00:11:54,690 --> 00:11:56,840
The Beauty Pearl Society is
certainly well-informed.

213
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,480
Now that you're here,

214
00:11:58,720 --> 00:11:59,480
it won't be long

215
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,679
before everyone else does.

216
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:02,919
I never would have expected

217
00:12:02,919 --> 00:12:04,159
the legendary market master

218
00:12:05,159 --> 00:12:06,559
to be hiding in a place like this.

219
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,360
Like I said,

220
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:10,159
the person you're looking for

221
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,120
isn't me.

222
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,120
It's been three months.

223
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:16,240
The chaos hasn't ended,

224
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,600
and there's no winner.

225
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,720
Everyone is doing whatever they can

226
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,000
to grab a larger stake.

227
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:24,240
Isn't that just how the market works?

228
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,960
Is the Beauty Pearl Society

229
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,879
entering the fray
just to watch the world burn?

230
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,960
We know you're holding a winning hand.

231
00:12:31,679 --> 00:12:32,879
We're just curious

232
00:12:32,919 --> 00:12:33,840
when exactly

233
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:35,200
you plan to play it.

234
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,519
Like I told you, handsome.

235
00:12:40,679 --> 00:12:42,480
You've got the wrong guy.

236
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:46,759
By the way,

237
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:48,159
what does Miss Rao

238
00:12:48,159 --> 00:12:50,519
plan to do once her plan is in motion?

239
00:12:59,900 --> 00:13:00,559
(Yinyu Technology)

240
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:01,360
Boss,

241
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:03,159
everything is ready.

242
00:13:14,519 --> 00:13:15,399
Good work, everyone.

243
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:17,799
Let the war begin.

244
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:19,559
(Right after Yinyu Technology)

245
00:13:19,559 --> 00:13:20,720
(acquired a six percent stake)

246
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:21,879
(in Bosi Real Estate,)

247
00:13:21,879 --> 00:13:23,320
(Lysen Group followed suit,)

248
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,600
(purchasing over eight percent)

249
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,519
(of Bosi's shares.)

250
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:27,080
(According to regulatory requirements,)

251
00:13:27,080 --> 00:13:28,000
(an acquirer must disclose)

252
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,279
(their holdings once they exceed)

253
00:13:29,279 --> 00:13:30,399
(the five percent threshold.)

254
00:13:30,399 --> 00:13:31,279
(This takeover battle)

255
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:34,159
(is now drawing significant
industry attention.)

256
00:13:35,159 --> 00:13:37,440
(Lysen, Bosi Top 10 Shareholders, Yinyu)
Mr. Jiang, what's our next buy-in?

257
00:13:47,919 --> 00:13:49,200
Let's see how far they'll go.

258
00:13:49,740 --> 00:13:51,100
(Yinyu)

259
00:13:51,559 --> 00:13:52,279
Boss!

260
00:13:52,279 --> 00:13:53,480
We've secured nine percent.

261
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:56,480
Great work.

262
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,799
Pengyu, that was beautifully done.

263
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:01,970
Not as beautiful as you.

264
00:14:05,460 --> 00:14:10,020
(Yinyu 9%)

265
00:14:10,250 --> 00:14:11,879
The competition has
reached nine percent.

266
00:14:12,100 --> 00:14:14,500
(Yinyu 9%)

267
00:14:24,279 --> 00:14:25,399
Push it to twelve percent.

268
00:14:26,159 --> 00:14:27,679
Stay focused, everyone.

269
00:14:27,679 --> 00:14:28,720
We're hitting twelve percent.

270
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:29,600
- Copy that.
- On it.

271
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,480
So far, you've both been playing it safe.

272
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,759
The numbers are tight.

273
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,600
You're just testing each other's limits.

274
00:14:53,159 --> 00:14:54,360
But moving forward,

275
00:14:54,919 --> 00:14:56,039
your real goal

276
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:57,360
is to overtake

277
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,520
(Yang Jinwan 14%)
Yang Jinwan's fourteen percent stake.

278
00:15:00,879 --> 00:15:01,759
(Breaking news.)

279
00:15:01,759 --> 00:15:03,960
(Yinyu Technology has increased
its stake in Bosi Real Estate)

280
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,039
(to nine percent.)

281
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:06,039
(Meanwhile, Lysen Group)

282
00:15:06,039 --> 00:15:07,759
(is gaining ground at twelve percent.)

283
00:15:07,799 --> 00:15:10,240
(The takeover battle
between these two giants for Bosi)

284
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,159
(is reaching a fever pitch,)

285
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:13,159
(closing in on the majority shareholder,)

286
00:15:13,159 --> 00:15:13,960
(Yang Jinwan.)

287
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:27,320
I've run the numbers.

288
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:30,600
Jiang Dongchao's acquisition fund
can't push past nineteen percent.

289
