in your feud.

578
00:30:00,519 --> 00:30:01,480
I'm only here today

579
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:03,880
to settle my own affairs.

580
00:30:05,319 --> 00:30:07,039
The snack street
renewal plan was halted.

581
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:09,279
The Green Building Materials
project was halted.

582
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:11,759
I was the one
who pushed for these projects,

583
00:30:12,210 --> 00:30:13,400
and now that they've stalled,

584
00:30:13,559 --> 00:30:14,599
I am responsible.

585
00:30:14,799 --> 00:30:15,680
I'm also aware

586
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:17,839
that Lysen Group's takeover of Bosi

587
00:30:17,839 --> 00:30:18,480
has reached

588
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,799
a critical stage.

589
00:30:20,039 --> 00:30:22,119
I know the company has no resources left

590
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:24,559
to help me restart these projects.

591
00:30:24,559 --> 00:30:25,279
That's why

592
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:28,359
I've come to you, Mr. Li.

593
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:30,240
I hope that you'll be able

594
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,640
to see the growth potential

595
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:33,720
in these projects.

596
00:30:34,559 --> 00:30:36,599
I want to ensure that

597
00:30:37,119 --> 00:30:38,119
these initiatives

598
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:39,920
which benefit Lysen,

599
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:41,300
these people, and even this city

600
00:30:42,279 --> 00:30:43,559
can continue to move forward.

601
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:49,599
(Green Building Materials Acquisition)
The Green Building Materials acquisition

602
00:30:50,119 --> 00:30:52,119
and the snack street renewal plan

603
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,480
both need funding to restart.

604
00:30:56,240 --> 00:30:56,960
I need

605
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,200
your support, Mr. Li.

606
00:31:31,079 --> 00:31:32,119
Mr. Pengyu, you're here.

607
00:31:32,559 --> 00:31:33,359
This way, please.

608
00:31:42,079 --> 00:31:42,680
Mr. Pengyu,

609
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:44,000
will you be having your usual?

610
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:45,519
It's a big day today.

611
00:31:45,519 --> 00:31:46,240
I'm celebrating.

612
00:31:46,319 --> 00:31:47,460
Let's have champagne instead.

613
00:31:47,799 --> 00:31:48,599
Understood.

614
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:53,720
Thank you.

615
00:31:58,440 --> 00:31:59,480
Do you remember this place?

616
00:32:02,079 --> 00:32:02,880
I don't.

617
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:07,440
This is where

618
00:32:07,440 --> 00:32:08,519
we first met.

619
00:32:09,559 --> 00:32:10,519
Right there at that bar.

620
00:32:17,240 --> 00:32:18,039
Ms. Bai,

621
00:32:18,559 --> 00:32:20,599
we're also optimistic
about Chuxia's future.

622
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:22,880
(Three Years Ago)
We're very much looking forward

623
00:32:23,039 --> 00:32:25,720
to entrusting
our consulting projects to Chuxia.

624
00:32:25,720 --> 00:32:26,680
Pour it.

625
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:27,440
Fill the glass.

626
00:32:30,519 --> 00:32:31,880
But I wonder

627
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,519
just how sincere you are, Ms. Bai.

628
00:32:33,519 --> 00:32:34,279
Exactly.

629
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:36,200
What's the rush?

630
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:37,440
Sincerity?

631
00:32:37,839 --> 00:32:39,160
Isn't she proving it right now?

632
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,160
She's full of it.

633
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:41,839
Right, show us what you've got.

634
00:32:41,839 --> 00:32:42,599
You guys...

635
00:32:43,079 --> 00:32:44,759
you should learn how to treat a lady.

636
00:32:44,759 --> 00:32:47,039
Down these three glasses,

637
00:32:47,599 --> 00:32:48,720
and then we'll talk.

638
00:32:51,359 --> 00:32:52,480
Drink up, Ms. Bai.

639
00:32:53,160 --> 00:32:54,039
Don't be shy.

640
00:32:59,279 --> 00:33:00,000
Finish them all,

641
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:01,480
and we can move on to the next step.

642
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:03,119
That's enough, you lot.

643
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:05,000
Never seen a girl drink before?

644
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:06,359
Here, I'll drink for her.

645
00:33:10,039 --> 00:33:10,920
Mr. Pengyu.

646
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:14,440
Is this sincere enough?

647
00:33:14,759 --> 00:33:15,759
Yes, more than enough.

648
00:33:15,759 --> 00:33:17,279
Can someone get me some tissues?

649
00:33:17,279 --> 00:33:18,039
Sure, right away.

650
00:33:22,839 --> 00:33:23,640
Hello.

651
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:25,390
Xian Pengyu from Yuanjian Capital.

652
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:27,279
From now on,
you'll be handling my accounts.

653
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:29,440
Hello.

654
00:33:29,450 --> 00:33:30,590
Bai Liangliang, from Chuxia.

655
00:33:32,079 --> 00:33:33,680
(I never would have guessed back then)

656
00:33:34,079 --> 00:33:35,680
that a single drink

657
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:37,160
could lead to a deep bond between us

658
00:33:38,319 --> 00:33:39,400
that lasted all these years.

659
00:34:06,640 --> 00:34:07,400
Liangliang...

660
00:34:07,400 --> 00:34:09,320
Memories are worthless to me.

661
00:34:11,239 --> 00:34:12,320
We're just friends.

662
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,840
At most, we're friends with benefits.

663
00:34:18,360 --> 00:34:19,519
If you're about to tell me

664
00:34:19,519 --> 00:34:20,679
that you've fallen for me,

665
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:22,679
or that

666
00:34:23,480 --> 00:34:25,079
you want me to be your girlfriend,

667
00:34:26,039 --> 00:34:27,280
don't bother.

668
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:30,559
Flowers,

669
00:34:31,119 --> 00:34:31,920
champagne,

670
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:33,440
fancy restaurants,

671
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:35,480
none of that

672
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:37,039
interests me in the slightest.

673
00:34:37,719 --> 00:34:38,960
I'm no Cinderella.

674
00:34:41,000 --> 00:34:42,639
Ms. Bai, you're overthinking it.

675
00:34:43,750 --> 00:34:45,719
I have zero intention
of starting a relationship.

676
00:34:46,719 --> 00:34:48,320
I simply wanted

677
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:50,360
to take you out for a casual meal today.

678
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:51,559
That's all.

679
00:34:53,119 --> 00:34:54,360
Well, that's even better then.

680
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,400
Cheers.

681
00:34:59,599 --> 00:35:00,440
To our partnership.

682
00:35:52,140 --> 00:35:55,900
=Episode 20=
(Wounds)

683
00:35:56,461 --> 00:35:58,901
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

684
00:35:58,901 --> 00:36:05,101
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

685
00:36:05,861 --> 00:36:09,061
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

686
00:36:09,061 --> 00:36:13,581
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

687
00:36:13,581 --> 00:36:21,101
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

688
00:36:21,101 --> 00:36:25,021
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

689
00:36:25,021 --> 00:36:29,061
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

690
00:36:29,061 --> 00:36:32,581
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

691
00:36:32,581 --> 00:36:36,541
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

692
00:36:36,541 --> 00:36:40,701
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

693
00:36:40,701 --> 00:36:44,901
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

694
00:36:44,901 --> 00:36:48,701
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

695
00:36:48,701 --> 00:36:52,781
♪Keep walking through the light♪

696
00:36:52,781 --> 00:36:56,981
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

697
00:36:56,981 --> 00:37:03,301
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

698
00:37:20,421 --> 00:37:27,061
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

699
00:37:27,061 --> 00:37:30,901
♪An apology that came too late♪

700
00:37:30,901 --> 00:37:35,541
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

701
00:37:35,621 --> 00:37:43,021
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

702
00:37:43,021 --> 00:37:47,101
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

703
00:37:47,101 --> 00:37:51,181
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

704
00:37:51,181 --> 00:37:55,181
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

705
00:37:55,181 --> 00:37:58,941
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

706
00:37:58,941 --> 00:38:03,141
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

707
00:38:03,141 --> 00:38:07,301
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

708
00:38:07,301 --> 00:38:11,021
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

709
00:38:11,021 --> 00:38:15,061
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

710
00:38:15,061 --> 00:38:19,101
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

711
00:38:19,101 --> 00:38:25,301
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
